# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID for the SPA build.
# Create at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# (Web application type). Add http://localhost:5173 and your deployed
# origin to Authorized JavaScript origins. In Testing mode, also add
# each allowed user's email to the OAuth consent screen test users list.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the real value; .env.local
# is gitignored.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
